
听说使用visual模式可以很方便地进行剪切黏贴

press v and then move the cursor to cover the text you want to operate, the press y to copy it, or press d to cut it

we can test the text replace function here as well.
try to replace see to saw .
use 
:%s/see/saw
从某行之后开始替换
:15,$s/see/saw

以下是测试区域：

================================================================================
123444444
1213放
ioasndfa sdlfjasldjf  sldfj ;asdljfa 
alsdkjflajsdlfjasldjsldf 
alsdjfla
拉伸件代发件速度快解可以很方便地进行剪切黏贴

